{"word":"ἀσκελής","slug":"ἀσκελής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀσκελής</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>α</el> <a href='S:euphonic'>euphon.</a> , <a href='S:σκέλλω'><el>σκέλλω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>dried up, withered</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:neuter'>neut.</a> <el>ἀσκελές</el> as <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <i>toughly, obstinately, stubbornly</i>, <el>ἀσκελὲς αἰεί</el> <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>; so, <el>ἀσκελέως αἰεί</el> <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}